company_description: Kry offers digital healthcare services that help patients to make active choices about their health in partnership with public and private healthcare professionals. It specializes in the fields of healthcare, E-health, and Digital health. Kry was founded in 2015 and headquartered in Stockholms Lan, Sweden.
